# fse-core — repository ignore rules
# This is a documentation/methodology repository: no build, no artifacts.
# These rules keep local-only and secret-bearing files out of commits.

# Machine-local Claude Code settings.
# The AI wiring (.claude/instructions.md) stays tracked; only local settings are ignored.
.claude/settings.local.json

# Secret-scan local pattern files — A4/A5 material (retired-credential strings,
# deploy profile names). Loaded at runtime by tooling/secret-scan/pre-push.sh.
# Never committed. See tooling/secret-scan/README.md.
.fse-secrets-patterns

# Secret-scan test artifacts — planted, obviously-fake secrets used to validate
# the hook. Untracked by construction so a test can never enter a commit.
*.fse-test

# OS / editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~
